  <description><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Villa Fraulo has a great location. It’s in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47}" title="Amalfi Coast">Ravello</a> close to the main square, Piazza Vescovado, so you won’t have to go far to explore the town’s sights. The hotel used to be the residence of the Cortese family so it’s got plenty of history and character. There’s a beautiful stone fireplace in the dining room that dates back to the 19th Century.</p>
<p>We love spending time on the hotel’s terrace where you can order a classic cocktail or glass of prosecco and chill out on one of the loungers. If you want to relax even more, the wellness centre's great. There’s a small pool with sea views and you can book in for a massage (treatments are payable locally).</p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 1 hour 10 mins by private car from Naples airport.</p>]]></description>
