  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Hotel Villa Fraulo is one of the most beautiful hotels in Ravello. It has plenty of history and character with classic rooms and a gorgeous stone fireplace in the dining room. The sea views are unavoidable with private balconies overlooking the ocean and a large terrace with loungers and umbrellas.</p>]]></listingDescription>
